collectionMetadata.name: Renting Out of Flats 2023
collectionMetadata.description: Market rental rates by approval date. The rental should be taken as indicative only as the rental agreed between the flat owners and tenants are dependent on many factors. The rental is based on the declaration by the flat owner. HDB does not verify the accuracy of the data.

datasetMetadata.name: Renting Out of Flats 2024 (CSV)
datasetMetadata.description:
Market rental rates by approval date. The rental should be taken as indicative only as the rental agreed between the flat owners and tenants are dependent on many factors. The rental is based on the declaration by the flat owner. HDB does not verify the accuracy of the data.

Data starts from 2021. Due to technical issues previously, this is the latest version of the Renting Out of Flats 2023 dataset, and further updates will be continued here.
